The,mail,Email,Marketing,API,is,a,REST,based,email,delivery,and,tracking,service,that,allows,users,to,add,email,list,management,functionality,into,other,applications,The,API,allows,users,to,extend,the,functionality,of,their,applications,by,integrating,email,marketing,components,to,their,existing,services,Use,of,the,mail,API,requires,installation,of,the,Tessitura,platform,The,overall,service,provided,by,mail,is,tied,to,the,Tessitura,platform,Tessitura,focuses,on,identify,patron,segments,based,on,their,transactional,history,while,mail,identifying,segments,based,on,patron,engagement,history,This,is,a,RESTful,web,service,with,a,JSON,response,type,The,mail,API,requires,an,account,with,service,and,an,API,key,for,access